All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeBlock
    Represents a Markdown code block with language specification and proper escaping.
    CodeBlock.Builder
    Builder class for creating CodeBlock instances.
    Element
    Abstract class representing a Markdown element.
    Header
    Represents a Markdown header with a specified level (1-6) and content.
    Header.Builder
    Builder class for creating Header instances.
    Image
    Represents a Markdown image with URL and alt text.
    Image.Builder
    Builder class for creating Image instances.
    Link
    Represents a Markdown link with text, URL, and optional title.
    Link.Builder
    Builder class for creating Link instances.
    Lst
    Represents a Markdown list (ordered or unordered) with support for nested lists.
    Lst.Builder
    Builder class for creating Lst instances.
    Main
    Main class that demonstrates the usage of Markdown table generation.
    Quote
    Represents a Markdown quote that can span multiple lines and contain nested elements.
    Quote.Builder
    Builder class for creating Quote instances.
    Table
    Represents a Markdown table with rows and columns.
    Table.Builder
    Builder class for creating Table instances.
    Task
    Represents a Markdown task/checkbox item with support for nested elements.
    Task.Builder
    Builder class for creating Task instances.
    Text
    Represents plain text and its formatting variations in Markdown.
    Text.Builder
    Builder class for creating Text instances.
